        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 5. Micrograph of Stygarctus keralensis sp. nov., (A) DIC micrograph showing paired sub-cephalic pore/muscle attachment; (B) DIC micrograph showing minute spikes on third lateral processes; (C) light microscopy micrograph showing dorsal antero-lateral lobe; (D-F) multifocal DIC micrographs showing female gonopore and seminal receptacles; (G) ventral view of paratype female [MB/SBN/VD5]; (H) dorsal view of paratype female [MB/SBN/VD3]." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4956237/files/figure.png" .

