        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 7. Scanning electron micrographs of Stygarctus keralensis sp. nov., (A) Dorsal view of habitus; (B) ventro-lateral view of habitus; (C) caudal plate showing female gonopore; (D) micro-spines on the first lateral processes. fg, female gonopore; o, opening of seminal receptacle; a, anus; ms1, micro-spines on first lateral processes." ;
